1>Open the project
2>go to admin settings
3>click on workflow scheme
4>Open the workflow where you to apply these settings
5>click on edit workflow
6>select the transition where you want to apply these condition
7> now click on condition
8>Add condition
9>Select simple scripted condition
10> Note -> if the closed date is greater than today date
11>add below condition
cfValues[“Closed Date”] > new Date()
12> Now follow the same thing for the other transition but add the below condition
cfValues[“Closed Date”] < new Date()
13>Now publish the workflow and test

